.It server
The server.
.It nickname
The new nickname.
.El
.\" NOTICE
.Ss NOTICE
This command is used to send a message to a global channel notice.
.Bd -literal -offset indent
NOTICE server channel message\\n
.Ed
.Pp
Parameters:
.Bl -tag -compact -width PARAMETERXXXX -offset indent
